snippet.title: I made an INSANELY scary game inspired by P.T. [TRAILER]
snippet.description:
Experience the terror of a psychological atmospheric indie horror game that seamlessly merges the chilling aspects of SCP-087, P.T. (Silent Hill), and Resident Evil. Unravel the mysteries, confront unspeakable evil, and try to stay alive as you navigate this blood-curdling infinite stairwell. The darkness awaits. #ScaryHorrorGame #SCP087 #PTSilentHill 

► Twitter - https://twitter.com/MrPeanutBelly
